f=Engineering/raj/custom/api-standards/assets/api-contract-checklist.md · h1:API Contract Checklist raj/api-standards=Run endpoint/surface. Protocol specifics (REST/GraphQL/gRPC) stack-profile; invariant. · h2:Auth=Authentication non-public route, Authorization checked PER-OBJECT, per-route (IDOR guard), Secrets/tokens never URLs, logs, error bodies · h2:Versioning=[ ] Version explicit, Breaking change (removed field type change semantic change) version bump, live contract mutated, Additive-only changes stay within version · h2:Error shape=Single error envelope (code message detail), stable machine-readable code, Correct status codes; never 200-wrapping-an-error, stack traces internal structure leaked untrusted callers · h2:Bounds=List endpoints paginate; unbounded responses (cost DoS cypher L10), Limits enforced server-side · h2:Contract tests (quinn gate evidence)=Request response shape pinned tests, Breaking change fails CI, production client · h2:Integration=Resource shape reflects dana's data model, Deep/N+1-prone access data-access-discipline (not raw queries handler), Security-relevant surface aegis secure-code-review